title: Mighty Sam McClain - 1999 - Soul Survivor (2008 SACD 24 88.2) FL
description:
Mighty Sam McClain - 1999 - Soul Survivor (2008)
SACD rip at 24 bits, 88.2 KHz

Good overview of McClain's four Audioquest releases, along with two previously unreleased tracks. "Keep on Movin'" should have been included, as its catchy arrangements are ideal bumper music for a late night TV talk show. (AllMusic)
